name: RGB-Side: Rancid (Audio/Visual)
description: CW: Flashing Images. Audio visual re-release of 2015 Track Rancid from my RGB-Side EP. I was experimenting with glitching in both images and audio at the time. The visual is a compilation of several gifs I made to accompany the project. I was deep in grief and feeling disconnected from reality and that's reflected in the raw production and lack of clarity in the music. T: @joshuafry
